<td class="mbox-text" style="">The examples and perspective in this article <b>may not represent a <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:WikiProject_Countering_systemic_bias" title="Wikipedia:WikiProject Countering systemic bias">worldwide view</a> of the subject</b>. Please <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Terrorism&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Terrorism&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">improve this article</a> or discuss the issue on the <a href="/wiki/Talk:Terrorism" title="Talk:Terrorism">talk page</a>.</td>
</tr>
