<li><a href="http://www.newsweek.com/id/183660/output/print" class="external text" title="http://www.newsweek.com/id/183660/output/print" rel="nofollow">"Terror on the Streets of New York, Take One"</a> by David Wallace-Wells, <i>Newsweek</i>, February 16 2009</li>
</ul>
