<li id="cite_note-Crenshaw38-62">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Crenshaw38_62-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Crenshaw38_62-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Crenshaw38_62-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> Crenshaw, Martha, <i>Terrorism in Context</i>, p. 38</li>
<li id="cite_note-Crenshaw44-63"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Crenshaw44_63-0" title="">^</a></b> Crenshaw, p. 44.</li>
<li id="cite_note-64"><b><a href="#cite_ref-64" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/front/etc/today.html" class="external text" title="http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/front/etc/today.html" rel="nofollow">frontline: al qaeda's new front: al qaeda today | PBS</a></li>
