<li id="cite_note-66"><b><a href="#cite_ref-66" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/enemywithin/reality/al-banna.html" class="external text" title="http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/enemywithin/reality/al-banna.html" rel="nofollow">Frontline: the enemy within: new reality: the man turned away | PBS</a></li>
