<li id="cite_note-Schmid_Terrorism_Definition-68"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Schmid_Terrorism_Definition_68-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20070627231104/http://www.unodc.org/unodc/terrorism_definitions.html" class="external text" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20070627231104/http://www.unodc.org/unodc/terrorism_definitions.html" rel="nofollow">"Academic Consensus Definition of "Terrorism," Schmid 1988, United Nations website"</a>. Archived from <a href="http://www.unodc.org/unodc/terrorism_definitions.html" class="external text" title="http://www.unodc.org/unodc/terrorism_definitions.html" rel="nofollow">the original</a> on 2007-06-27<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://web.archive.org/web/20070627231104/http://www.unodc.org/unodc/terrorism_definitions.html" class="external free" title="http://web.archive.org/web/20070627231104/http://www.unodc.org/unodc/terrorism_definitions.html" rel="nofollow">http://web.archive.org/web/20070627231104/http://www.unodc.org/unodc/terrorism_definitions.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Academic+Consensus+Definition+of+%22Terrorism%2C%22+Schmid+1988%2C+United+Nations+website&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20070627231104%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.unodc.org%2Funodc%2Fterrorism_definitions.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Terrorism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>. For more detailed information, see: Schmid, Jongman et al. <i>Political terrorism: a new guide to actors, authors, concepts, data bases, theories, and literature</i>. Amsterdam: North Holland, Transaction Books, 1988. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1412804698" class="internal">ISBN 1412804698</a></li>
